        <!-- Strategy Recommendations -->
        <div class="section">
            <h3 class="section-title">Strategic Recommendations</h3>
            <div class="strategy-container">
    <div class="strategy-item">
        <h4 class="strategy-title">Launch Off-Peak Pricing Discounts</h4>
        <p>Utilize MaxPan's time-based pricing to offer 10-15% discounts during consistently underused off-peak hours (e.g., 8 AM–9 AM, 2 PM–4 PM, 8 PM–10 PM). This will help redistribute volume, increase utilization (currently at only 18%), and drive incremental revenue from otherwise idle machines.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="strategy-item">
        <h4 class="strategy-title">Activate Lapsed Customers with WhatsApp-Only Coupons</h4>
        <p>Since 79.2% of your customers are lapsed and less than 21% return within 90 days, launch a WhatsApp campaign offering a time-limited 20% discount coupon for either a wash or dry cycle. Target the “Potential” and “Lapsed” customers and reinforce visits by promoting the branded laundry bag as a loyalty incentive.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="strategy-item">
        <h4 class="strategy-title">Promote Dryer Usage During Peak Washer Hours</h4>
        <p>Dryer utilization is critically low (12%) compared to washers (28%). During peak hours like 10 AM, 11 AM, and 6 PM, offer bundled deals (e.g., “Dry for BRL 12.90 with a Wash”) to convert more wash-only users into full-cycle customers and balance out machine usage.</p>
    </div>
